				<td colspan="2"><span>k i have limited my choices down to a bard/cleric duo or a cleric/bst duo...i am guessin posting this on a bard board i am going to get alot of bard/cleric votes heh so here is a bit of backround on what i want to be able to do with my duo..
<br />

<br />
 Ok i want a duo that can get good exp and lvl up all the way to 65 at a good pace(of course i plan on grouping and all.. im just saying i dont want to have to depend on a group to get good exp)... Not only do i want a duo that can exp all the way to 65, but also farm AAs/pp at 65.. i would also like my duo to be able to take on some big named mobs.. So with all that in mind which duo do you think would suite me the best out of those two?... Please dont post saying &quot;Pick the class you like more&quot; cause i like both the beastlord and bard pretty much the same and would have fun playing either.. I just need to know what duo would make what i want to do easier.</span></td>
